description: A dashboard for visualizing results from the k6.io load testing tool by groups,

azureLogAnalytics.query:
AppRequests
| extend  AppRoleName = replace_string(AppRoleName, "-staging", "")
| where _ResourceId has "f4edc7ff-4396-47be-bf14-90892e463848"
| where AppRoleName != "" 
| extend AppVersion = case(AppVersion in ("1.0.0.1", "1.0.0.0", "5.0.10", "3.1", "6.0.3"), "", AppVersion)
| where AppVersion != "" 
| summarize FirstRequest=min(TimeGenerated) by AppVersion, AppRoleName
| where $__timeFilter(FirstRequest)
| extend Release = 1
| order by FirstRequest asc

AppRequests
| extend  AppRoleName = replace_string(AppRoleName, "-staging", "")
| where _ResourceId has "0be01d84-8432-4558-9aba-ecd204a3ee61"
| where AppRoleName != "" 
| extend AppVersion = case(AppVersion in ("1.0.0.1", "1.0.0.0", "5.0.10", "3.1", "6.0.3"), "", AppVersion)
| where AppVersion != "" 
| summarize FirstRequest=min(TimeGenerated) by AppVersion, AppRoleName
| where $__timeFilter(FirstRequest)
| extend Release = 1
| order by FirstRequest asc

AppRequests
| extend  AppRoleName = replace_string(AppRoleName, "-staging", "")
| where _ResourceId !has "f4edc7ff-4396-47be-bf14-90892e463848" and _ResourceId !has "0be01d84-8432-4558-9aba-ecd204a3ee61"
| where AppRoleName != "" 
| extend AppVersion = case(AppVersion in ("1.0.0.1", "1.0.0.0", "5.0.10", "3.1", "6.0.3"), "", AppVersion)
| where AppVersion != "" 
| summarize FirstRequest=min(TimeGenerated) by AppVersion, AppRoleName
| where $__timeFilter(FirstRequest)
| extend Release = 1
| order by FirstRequest asc

panels.description: Grouped by 1 sec intervals and group name

azureLogAnalytics.query:
K6Test_CL
| extend TimeGenerated_ = unixtime_seconds_todatetime(tolong(timestamp_s))
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated_)
| where $__contains(group_s, $Group)
| where $__contains(url_s, $URL)
| where metric_name_s == $Measurement
| where $__contains(BuildDefinition_s, $Source)
| summarize P95=percentile(todouble(metric_value_s), 95) by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated_, 1s), Group=group_s
| order by TimeGenerated asc

panels.title: API response times - $Measurement  - over time by group

azureLogAnalytics.query:
K6Test_CL
| extend TimeGenerated_ = unixtime_seconds_todatetime(tolong(timestamp_s))
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated_)
| where $__contains(group_s, $Group) 
| where $__contains(url_s, $URL)

| summarize P95=percentile(todouble(metric_value_s), 95) by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated_, 1s), Url=url
| order by TimeGenerated asc
